request.description:
Verifikasi wajah karyawan.

Form-data:
- image (file)

Response (match):
{
  "status": "success",
  "data": {
    "match": true,
    "employee_id": "RAFIKA123",
    "name": "Rafika",
    "distance": 2.85,
    "threshold": 3.5,
    "confidence": "medium"
  }
}

Response (no match):
{
  "status": "success",
  "data": {
    "match": false,
    "reason": "Tidak ada wajah cocok.",
    "best_distance": 6.01,
    "threshold": 3.5
  }
}

Melihat daftar user yang sudah terdaftar beserta jumlah foto/embedding.

Response contoh:
{
  "status": "success",
  "data": [
    {
      "employee_id": "RAFIKA123",
      "name": "Rafika",
      "num_embeddings": 4
    },
    {
      "employee_id": "LINYI001",
      "name": "Lin Yi",
      "num_embeddings": 3
    }
  ]
}

Menghapus data wajah 1 karyawan dari database.

Path param:
- employee_id

Response jika berhasil:
{
  "status": "success",
  "data": {
    "deleted": true,
    "employee_id": "TEST123"
  }
}

Response jika tidak ditemukan (404):
{
  "detail": "User tidak ditemukan"
}
